            "value" : "ChillMate is gratis voor iedereen. Een fooi is een kleine, volledig optionele manier om bedankt te zeggen."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "ChillMate is intended for adults only." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "nl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "ChillMate is alleen bedoeld voor volwassenen."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "ChillMate saves an encrypted backup file to your iCloud Drive. Your data is encrypted before it leaves the app." : {
      "comment" : "A description of how the backup is encrypted.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "ChillMate saves an encrypted backup file to your iCloud Drive. Your data is encrypted before it leaves the app."
          }
        },
        "nl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "ChillMate slaat een versleuteld back-upbestand op in je iCloud Drive. Je gegevens worden versleuteld voor ze de app verlaten."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "ChillMate still works. Apple Health, notifications, location, and iCloud backup just make reminders, recovery, emergency messages, and restore easier." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "nl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "ChillMate werkt nog steeds. Apple Health, meldingen, locatie en iCloud-back-up maken herinneringen, herstel, noodberichten en terugzetten alleen makkelijker."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "ChillMate supports reflection, recovery, STI care, privacy, and emergency planning. It does not replace a clinician, diagnose conditions, decide whether something is safe, or recommend amounts, timing, or substance use." : {
      "comment" : "A disclaimer for ChillMate.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "ChillMate supports reflection, recovery, STI care, privacy, and emergency planning. It does not replace a clinician, diagnose conditions, decide whether something is safe, or recommend amounts, timing, or substance use."
          }
        },
        "nl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "ChillMate ondersteunt reflectie, herstel, soa-zorg, privacy en noodplanning. Het vervangt geen arts, stelt geen aandoeningen vast, bepaalt niet of iets veilig is en beveelt geen hoeveelheden, timing of middelengebruik aan."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "ChillMate supports reflection, recovery, STI care, privacy, and emergency planning. It does not replace a clinician, diagnose conditions, decide whether something is safe, or recommend amounts, timing, or substance use. Its information is drawn from verified, official public-health sources and is updated over time as those sources change. ChillMate and its maker are not liable in any way for decisions made using the app. If someone may be in immediate danger, call local emergency services." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "ChillMate supports reflection, recovery, STI care, privacy, and emergency planning. It does not replace a clinician, diagnose conditions, decide whether something is safe, or recommend amounts, timing, or substance use. Its information is drawn from verified, official public-health sources and is updated over time as those sources change. ChillMate and its maker are not liable in any way for decisions made using the app. If someone may be in immediate danger, call local emergency services."
          }
        },
        "nl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "ChillMate ondersteunt reflectie, herstel, soa-zorg, privacy en noodplanning. Het vervangt geen zorgverlener, stelt geen diagnoses, bepaalt niet of iets veilig is en raadt geen hoeveelheden, timing of middelengebruik aan. De informatie is afkomstig uit geverifieerde, officiële volksgezondheidsbronnen en wordt na verloop van tijd bijgewerkt wanneer die bronnen veranderen. ChillMate en de maker zijn op geen enkele manier aansprakelijk voor beslissingen die met de app worden genomen. Als iemand mogelijk in direct gevaar is, bel dan de lokale hulpdiensten."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "ChillMate supports safer decisions, but it is not a substitute for medical, legal, or emergency care." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "nl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "ChillMate ondersteunt veiligere beslissingen, maar is geen vervanging voor medische, juridische of noodzorg."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "ChillMate uses Dynamic Type, edge-swipe back navigation, VoiceOver labels on key controls, and reduced animation options for high-stress moments." : {
      "comment" : "A description of the accessibility features of ChillMate.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
