    "Consent can be changed or withdrawn at any time. If a memory gap or consent concern appears later, use panic support, trusted contact, GGD, CSG, or emergency help." : {
      "comment" : "A description of consent.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Consent can be changed or withdrawn at any time. If a memory gap or consent concern appears later, use panic support, trusted contact, GGD, CSG, or emergency help."
          }
        },
        "nl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Toestemming kan op elk moment worden veranderd of ingetrokken. Als er later een geheugengat of zorg over toestemming opduikt, gebruik dan paniekhulp, vertrouwenscontact, GGD, CSG of noodhulp."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Contact GGD, huisarts, or hospital as soon as possible. PEP works best when started quickly and is generally time limited to 72 hours." : {
