    "If any of these are happening, do not wait for the app. Call 112 in the Netherlands or your local emergency number." : {
      "comment" : "A warning message that appears when the user has selected one or more emergency red flags.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "If any of these are happening, do not wait for the app. Call 112 in the Netherlands or your local emergency number."
          }
        },
        "nl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Als een van deze dingen gebeurt, wacht dan niet op de app. Bel 112 in Nederland of je lokale noodnummer."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "If anything feels unclear, contact your prescriber, GGD, or pharmacist before relying on the plan." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "nl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Als iets onduidelijk voelt, neem dan contact op met je voorschrijver, GGD of apotheker voor je op het plan vertrouwt."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "If ChillMate has helped you feel a little safer or more in control, a small tip is a lovely way to say thanks. Every bit goes straight back into keeping the app running, updated, and free for everyone." : {
      "comment" : "A description of the benefits of tipping for ChillMate.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "If ChillMate has helped you feel a little safer or more in control, a small tip is a lovely way to say thanks. Every bit goes straight back into keeping the app running, updated, and free for everyone."
          }
        },
        "nl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Als ChillMate je heeft geholpen je iets veiliger of meer in controle te voelen, is een kleine fooi een mooie manier om bedankt te zeggen. Alles gaat rechtstreeks terug naar het draaiend, bijgewerkt en gratis houden van de app voor iedereen."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "If someone is unconscious, very confused, overheating, having chest pain, breathing oddly, or cannot be woken: call 112." : {
      "comment" : "A warning to call emergency services if someone is in danger.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "If someone is unconscious, very confused, overheating, having chest pain, breathing oddly, or cannot be woken: call 112."
          }
        },
        "nl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Als iemand bewusteloos is, erg verward, oververhit, pijn op de borst heeft, raar ademt of niet wakker te krijgen is: bel 112."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "If someone may be in immediate danger, call local emergency services." : {
      "comment" : "A warning message that instructs users to call emergency services if they are in immediate danger.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "If someone may be in immediate danger, call local emergency services."
          }
        },
        "nl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Als iemand in direct gevaar kan zijn, bel de lokale hulpdiensten."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "If there is chest pain, blue lips, seizure, or someone cannot be woken: call emergency services now." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "nl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Bij pijn op de borst, blauwe lippen, een toeval of als iemand niet wakker te krijgen is: bel nu de hulpdiensten."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "If there was a Chill, skipped Chill, sleep, or aftercare moment, you can add it when you feel ready." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "nl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Als er een Chill, overgeslagen Chill, slaap- of nazorgmoment was, kun je het toevoegen wanneer je er klaar voor bent."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "If you are unsafe, injured, cannot wake someone, or feel at risk, call 112 or a trusted person now." : {
      "comment" : "A warning message that appears if the user has not selected a safe state.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "If you are unsafe, injured, cannot wake someone, or feel at risk, call 112 or a trusted person now."
          }
        },
        "nl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Als je onveilig bent, gewond bent, iemand niet wakker krijgt of je in gevaar voelt, bel dan nu 112 of een vertrouwd persoon."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "If you feel pulled to continue, pause first. Check your body, water, food, sleep, consent, and whether someone trusted should know." : {
      "comment" : "A description of the purpose of the pause.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "If you feel pulled to continue, pause first. Check your body, water, food, sleep, consent, and whether someone trusted should know."
          }
        },
        "nl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Als je de drang voelt om door te gaan, pauzeer eerst. Check je lichaam, water, eten, slaap, toestemming en of iemand die je vertrouwt het moet weten."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "If you might hurt yourself or cannot stay safe. Call 113 or 0800-0113 in the Netherlands." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "nl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Als je jezelf zou kunnen pijn doen of niet veilig kunt blijven. Bel 113 of 0800-0113 in Nederland."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "If you need to step outside, that is always okay." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "nl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Als je naar buiten moet stappen, dat mag altijd."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "If you need urgent help, do not wait for the app. Call local emergency services." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "nl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Als je dringend hulp nodig hebt, wacht dan niet op de app. Bel de lokale hulpdiensten."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "If your results are in, add oral, genital, and anal results to ChillMate." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "nl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Als je uitslagen binnen zijn, voeg orale, genitale en anale uitslagen toe aan ChillMate."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Immediate danger, unconsciousness, or someone who cannot be woken. Call your local emergency number now." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "nl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
