    "Stimulant effects can strain the heart, reduce sleep, and increase impulsive decisions." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "nl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Stimulant-effecten kunnen het hart belasten, slaap verminderen en impulsieve beslissingen vergroten."
