    "The app can help organize notes for a conversation, but it cannot replace that conversation." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "nl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "De app kan helpen notities voor een gesprek te ordenen, maar kan dat gesprek niet vervangen."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The app mood follows your day" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "nl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "De sfeer van de app volgt je dag"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The fact that you are thinking about your health at all. That is not nothing." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "nl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Het feit dat je überhaupt aan je gezondheid denkt. Dat is niet niks."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The streak is yours. No one can see it but you, and it is real." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "nl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "De reeks is van jou. Niemand kan hem zien behalve jij, en hij is echt."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The things you protect about yourself quietly. They matter." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "nl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "De dingen die je stilletjes over jezelf beschermt. Die doen ertoe."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "There is no perfect way to do this. There is only what you actually do." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "nl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Er is geen perfecte manier om dit te doen. Er is alleen wat je echt doet."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "There is no version of care that is too small to count." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "nl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Er is geen vorm van zorg die te klein is om mee te tellen."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "These details keep your overview and timer estimates personal." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "These details keep your overview and timer estimates personal."
          }
        },
        "nl" : {
