            "value" : "Deze Chill"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This helps with your profile and timer estimates." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "nl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Dit helpt met je profiel en timerschattingen."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This is a reminder aid, not a PrEP prescription or dosage guide. Use it only if PrEP has been prescribed to you and your clinician has told you this schedule fits your body and sex type." : {
      "comment" : "A description of the PrEP guide.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "This is a reminder aid, not a PrEP prescription or dosage guide. Use it only if PrEP has been prescribed to you and your clinician has told you this schedule fits your body and sex type."
          }
        },
        "nl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Dit is een herinneringshulp, geen PrEP-voorschrift of doseringsgids. Gebruik het alleen als PrEP aan jou is voorgeschreven en je arts je heeft verteld dat dit schema past bij je lichaam en type seks."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This is a reminder window for checking wellbeing, water, rest, consent, and support. It does not estimate impairment or recommend timing, amounts, or use." : {
      "comment" : "A description of a static effect window.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "This is a reminder window for checking wellbeing, water, rest, consent, and support. It does not estimate impairment or recommend timing, amounts, or use."
          }
        },
        "nl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Dit is een herinneringsvenster om welzijn, water, rust, toestemming en steun te checken. Het schat geen verminderd vermogen in en beveelt geen timing, hoeveelheden of gebruik aan."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This is just a quiet check. You can close this and everything stays private." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "nl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Dit is gewoon een rustige check. Je kunt dit sluiten en alles blijft privé."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This is not medical advice. It does not recommend substances, amounts, or combinations." : {
      "localizations" : {
