        "nl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Ja, doorgaan"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "You already have a journal entry for today. Review your calendar when you want context." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "nl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Je hebt al een dagboekitem voor vandaag. Bekijk je kalender als je context wilt."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "You are allowed to move slowly. Slow is still moving." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "nl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Je mag langzaam gaan. Langzaam is nog steeds vooruit."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "You are creating space for recovery." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "nl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Je creëert ruimte voor herstel."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "You are not just tracking habits. You are learning what you need." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "nl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Je houdt niet alleen gewoontes bij. Je leert wat je nodig hebt."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "You are responsible for deciding what information you save and who you share it with." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "nl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Jij bent verantwoordelijk voor wat je opslaat en met wie je het deelt."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "You are worth checking in on, even when nothing is urgent." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "nl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Het is de moeite waard om bij jou in te checken, ook als er niets urgent is."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "You can be proud of choices that no one else will ever see." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "nl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Je mag trots zijn op keuzes die niemand anders ooit zal zien."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "You can delete logs, plans, STI tests, timers, risk checks, journal entries, and account data inside the app." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "nl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Je kunt logs, plannen, soa-tests, timers, risicochecks, dagboekitems en accountgegevens verwijderen in de app."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "You don't have to be doing great. How are you actually feeling?" : {
