            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Je lichaam onthoudt elke vriendelijke beslissing die je maakt, ook die je vergeet."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Your boundaries are still yours right now. Nothing has changed that." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "nl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Je grenzen zijn op dit moment nog steeds van jou. Niets heeft dat veranderd."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Your data is protected by default. You can also create an encrypted backup file that only you can open. Handy if you ever reinstall or switch phones." : {
